    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini, temporibus domni <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/1591"
                            >Benedicti</persName> summi pontificis et universalis <rs key="#Popes"
                            >pape</rs> in apostolica sacratissima beati Petri apostoli Domini sede
                        sitque imperante domno <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/261"
                            >Conrado</persName> piissimo perpetuo augusto <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperatore</rs> in Italia vero anno octavo, die viessimoquinto mensis
                        iunii, indicone secunda, <placeName>in loco qui dicitur
                            Stornatianus</placeName>, in tentorio domni <persName key="#Archbishops"
                            ref="#people/1590">Gebeardi</persName> sacratissimi <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1471"><placeName ref="#places/594"
                                >Ravennatis</placeName></orgName> predestinante Deo <rs
                            key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopi</rs>. Dum adessent quidem optimi atque
                        honestissimi nec non bone opinionis et laudabilis fame viri quorum nomina
                        hec sunt, idest: domnus <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Lambertus"
                                >Lambertus</name></persName> per Domini misericordiam <rs
                            key="#Abbots">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/1432">Sancti
                            Apollenaris quod vocatur ad Classem</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> et <persName key="#Abbots #Monks"
                            ref="#people/1574">Vuido</persName> Dei gratia <rs key="#Monks"
                            >monachus</rs>, et dudum monasterii <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Monks" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte
                            Marie quod vocatur ad <placeName ref="#places/4179"
                                >Pomposiam</placeName></orgName> abbas, et <persName key="#Count"
                                ><name ref="Bonifacius">Bonifacius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> et <persName key="#Count"><name ref="Hugo"
                                >Ugo</name></persName> comes quondam <persName key="#Count"><name
                                ref="Hubaldus">Ubaldi</name></persName> comitis filius atque
                            <persName key="#Marquis/duke"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petrus</name></persName> inclitus <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> et
                            <persName key="#Marquis/duke"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName> dux nobiles et <persName key="#Vir_inluster"
                                ><name ref="Teobaldus">Tedbaldus</name></persName> Deo annuente <rs
                            key="#Vir_inluster">illustris vir</rs> vice dominus et me presene
                            <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfo</name></persName>
                        Ravennate Christi misericordiam <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellione</rs> et
                        aliis. In nostra predictorum presencia refutavit <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Comitatus #Fodrum #Angaria #Tolls #Teloneum #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Beneficium">
                            <name ref="Hugo Bononiensis">Ugo</name></persName> nobilissimus comes
                            <placeName ref="#places/7">Bononiensis</placeName> per virgam quam
                        manibus detinebat domno Gebeardo reverentissimo predicto archiepiscopo
                        sueque Ravennati ecclesie et suis successoribus imperpetuum <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatum</rs> integrum <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus #Angaria #Tolls #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Fodrum #Teloneum #Beneficium"
                            ref="#estates/2458">
                            <placeName
                                key="#Comitatus #Angaria #Tolls #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Fodrum #Teloneum #Beneficium"
                                ref="#places/3513">Faventinum</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus <rs
                            key="#Angaria">angariis</rs> atque portaticis seu <rs
                            key="#Tolls #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">ripaticis</rs> sive
                            <rs key="#Fodrum">fodris</rs> nec non publicis funcionibus atque <rs
                            key="#Teloneum">tolloneis</rs> omnibus ad prefatum comitatum Faventinum
                        pertinentibus vel subviccentibus. Et tunc iam dictus domnus Gebeardus
                        predicte ecclesie archipresul hec ita accipiens et illico investivit
                        prenotatum Ugonem comitem Bononiensem de medietate iam nominati comitatus
                        Faventini cum omnibus ad ipsam medietatem pertinentibus in <rs
                            key="#Beneficium">beneficio</rs>. Hoc factum est sub die menseque et
                        indicione decunda suprascripta. Petrus dux in ac refutacione subscripsi.
                        Iohannes dux in hac refutacione ut supra legitur interfui et subscripsi.
                        Tedbaldus illustris vir in hac refutacione subscripsi vice dominus. Ego
                        Ravennas Rodulfus tabellio huius refutacionis scriptor post roboracionem
                        complevi, asolvi.</ab>
